				},
				{
					"id": "t00GedSmHCarvlYcd",
					"name": "Flawed Arts",
					"local_notes": "Due to your existence as a hybrid of Terran and Seaborn, your affinity for Originium Arts has been altered to a point of being completely nonfunctional.\n\nArts Casting/Magery cannot be taken as traits and spells cannot be learned.",
